# Douyin Copy Production Workflow

Use this skill for the user's complete production loop from assistant-collected scripts to publishable long-form drafts.

This skill coordinates four jobs:

1. Select scripts with `douyin-emotion-copy-scorer` / 「爆款文案筛选」.
